high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink then turn left and go to the table
Pick up the knife from behind the lotion bottle
Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the sink
Slice the potato that is on the counter
Turn around and take a step then turn right and take a step and then turn right and go to the small stand next to the counter
Stick the knife into the small stand
Turn right then turn left and go back to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter
Turn around and go towards the stove then turn left and go past the table then turn right then turn left and go to the microwave
Microwave the slice of potato then take it out of the microwave
Turn left then turn left again and go past the table then turn right and go to the small stand
Put the slice of potato on its end on the stand
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato on the stand next to the kitchen counter

high_descs: go to the right side of the white table
pick up the knife from that side of the table
take the knife to the counter to the left of the sink
slice the potato on the counter
go to the small black stand to the right of where you started at the table
stand the knife up by its tip on the black stand
go back to the counter where you sliced the potato
pick up a potato slice
take the slice to the microwave
warm the slice in the microwave then remove
take the cooked potato slice to the black stand
put the slice on the stand
anns.task_desc: put a cooked slice of potato on the black stand in the corner

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink, then turn left and step forward to the table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn around, then turn left to face the kitchen counter.
Cut the potato below the cup into slices
Turn around, step forward, turn right, step forward and turn right again to face a side table.
Stand the knife upright next to the salt shaker on the side table.
Return to the kitchen counter with the sliced potato.
Pick up the center slice of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the edge of the table, then turn left, walk towards the trash can, and then step right to be center with the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the potato inside to heat up for a few seconds, then remove the potato.
Return to the side table where the knife is standing upright.
Put the potato in your mouth and eat it.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a potato in the microwave and eat it.
